703659f-b.text:
(1)
Clinton Street, east side, north from Joralemon Street. Also seen is 159-173 Joralemon Street, north side, east from Clinton Street. (The Wheelock Home is at 161 Joralemon Street). The 10-story building at the left, belongs to the B.M.T Corp. Also seen at the left, is
the Spencer Memorial Presbyterian Church.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, showing a closer view of 161 Joralemon Street.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection,
(3)
The same, showing the N.E. corner now vacant, giving a clear view of
the church.
February 22, 1930.
L. Sperr.  NO REPRODUCTIONS.
